{"tid":2009563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問森奈奈子(會員#31623)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?","createTime":"2020-05-09T23:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T06:41:03.000Z","uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3be3278644947059e91e83544dc3f55d6abb9be","tid":2009563,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T23:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c311ce4520d78de58fcd113ce0b33ae99d45657","tid":2009563,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">老鳳一開po，所有食花生的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，「老鳳，你今日又殺咗幾多隻狗？」他不回答，自言自語，「大家睇住啦，分化狗永遠唔撚敢入以下嘅post反駁老鳳，佢地真係支共主力」，便開多個po屈班人做分化狗當駁咗。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又係度推人去死啦！」老鳳睜大眼睛說，「我係提倡緊全民勇武&hellip;&hellip;」「全民勇武？日日見你係啲po度叫人打狗殺狗，但係有行動就唔見你岀手，全民勇武唔包你自己？」老鳳便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「提倡全民勇武，不算是推人去死&hellip;&hellip;只係我無資格帶頭，無話過唔喺後面玩狙&hellip;&hellip;抗爭者的事，能算是推人去死麼」接連便是難懂的話，甚麼「有我係度隻狗死硬」，甚麼「捷克嘅係scorpion非常好用嘅槍」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來，連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdYfLXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdYfLXw.png&h=2f645353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3xXmHV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3xXmHV.png&h=ce7dfffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiooneH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiooneH.png&h=a27668c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFuDrg9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFuDrg9.png&h=008b0eb8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}